videos.title: Try Down Bad
videos.description: In 'Argentina: #IRCs21' the artists have carefully crafted a AFA medallion and framed it in a recognizable trophy like design. Interactive NFT's visually adjust according to Argentina's performance; at one point the shield will shine bright in a grand and sparkling golden frame when the team wins, its standard setting when there is a tie, and if losing, turns to a rainy bronze reflection of a lost match.
